snippet.title: DOFUS - Trailer
snippet.description:
DOFUS is a massively multiplayer online role-playing game specializing in tactical, turn-based strategy.

Test your tactical skill by stepping into one of 15 unique classes. DOFUS offers an unusual turn-based, 2D fight system that puts you in control of a character you can build and customize while facing off against a universe of strange and colorful monsters or struggle for dominance against other players.

http://www.dofus.com/en/discovery
DOFUS is an MMORPG produced by Ankama
